  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344410/extras/d76e42a18b1064a8a1a3904b69a468fa.poster.avif?t=1693593115\" width=624 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344410/extras/d76e42a18b1064a8a1a3904b69a468fa.webm?t=1693593115\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344410/extras/d76e42a18b1064a8a1a3904b69a468fa.mp4?t=1693593115\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Welcome to Danger in Body, the turn-based tower defense game that will put your strategic skills to the test! In this thrilling game, you are a cell in the human body that must defend itself against a dangerous virus invasion.<br><br>Each round is an epic battle, with increasingly challenging waves of enemies. You must use your resources wisely to build towers and fortifications that will help stop the viruses' advance.<br><br>But it's not just about building towers that will ensure your victory. You must also stay vigilant, using your intelligence and tactical ability to defeat the enemies. With each new wave of viruses, new challenges and obstacles will be presented, testing your ability to think quickly and adapt to difficult situations.<br><br>With vivid and exciting graphics, a pulsating soundtrack, and addictive gameplay, \"Danger in Body\" is a game that will keep you entertained and hooked for hours on end. You are the last hope of the human body - so get ready to fight for your right to live!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344410/extras/d76e42a18b1064a8a1a3904b69a468fa.poster.avif?t=1693593115\" width=624 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344410/extras/d76e42a18b1064a8a1a3904b69a468fa.webm?t=1693593115\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344410/extras/d76e42a18b1064a8a1a3904b69a468fa.mp4?t=1693593115\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Welcome to Danger in Body, the turn-based tower defense game that will put your strategic skills to the test! In this thrilling game, you are a cell in the human body that must defend itself against a dangerous virus invasion.<br><br>Each round is an epic battle, with increasingly challenging waves of enemies. You must use your resources wisely to build towers and fortifications that will help stop the viruses' advance.<br><br>But it's not just about building towers that will ensure your victory. You must also stay vigilant, using your intelligence and tactical ability to defeat the enemies. With each new wave of viruses, new challenges and obstacles will be presented, testing your ability to think quickly and adapt to difficult situations.<br><br>With vivid and exciting graphics, a pulsating soundtrack, and addictive gameplay, \"Danger in Body\" is a game that will keep you entertained and hooked for hours on end. You are the last hope of the human body - so get ready to fight for your right to live!",
